cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel pruning method for compressing neural networks. It also involves training and testing deep learning models on datasets such as CIFAR10 and ImageNet. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the models are tested on image classification tasks. Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper deals with neural networks and their optimization. Finally, it may also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper proposes a method for compressing neural networks by removing entire filters and neurons.
